《'''香港研究'''》（{{lang-en|Hong Kong Studies}}）是一本關於[[香港學|香港學]]的[[同行評審|同行評審]]、中英雙語出版學術期刊。期刊每半年出版一次，以跨學科領域研究香港的學術文章為主<ref>{{cite web |title=RETI/REAO About Hong Kong studies |url=https://www.bib.uab.cat/human/acreditacions/planes/publiques/revistes/revistesideng.php?area=eao&menuidioma=eng&idrev=770 |website=Humanities Library - Department of Translation and Interpreting & East Asian Studies |publisher=Autonomous University of Barcelona |access-date=2021-01-10 |archive-date=2021-01-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210116100125/https://www.bib.uab.cat/human/acreditacions/planes/publiques/revistes/revistesideng.php?area=eao&menuidioma=eng&idrev=770 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。期刊由香港中文大學出版社出版，中大英文系主編<ref>{{cite web |title=[CFP] Hong Kong Studies: A Bilingual Journal |url=https://hksi.ubc.ca/cfp-hong-kong-studies-a-bilingual-journal/ |website=Hong Kong Studies Initiative |publisher=University of British Columbia |access-date=2021-01-04 |archive-date=2021-01-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210116100209/https://hksi.ubc.ca/cfp-hong-kong-studies-a-bilingual-journal/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Resources Guide to Hong Kong Studies |url=https://guides.library.utoronto.ca/c.php?g=463748&p=3173992 |website=University of Toronto Libraries |access-date=2021-01-10 |archive-date=2021-01-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210116100118/https://guides.library.utoronto.ca/c.php?g=463748&p=3173992 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=Interview: Hong Kong History Project’s Vivian Kong on uncovering the city’s rich and ‘incredibly varied’ history |url=https://hongkongfp.com/2018/05/27/interview-hong-kong-history-projects-vivian-kong-uncovering-citys-rich-incredibly-varied-history/ |access-date=2021-01-10 |work=Hong Kong Free Press |date=2018-05-27 |archive-date=2021-01-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210116100118/https://hongkongfp.com/2018/05/27/interview-hong-kong-history-projects-vivian-kong-uncovering-citys-rich-incredibly-varied-history/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

